      <num>SEC. 2.7</num>
      <heading>Same—Authorized rentals or leases</heading>
      <content>
        <p>Nothing stated in Sec. 2.4 to 2.6 shall be construed to apply to lawful and legally authorized rentals or leases of
               city equipment, tools or paraphernalia.</p>
        <p>(Ord. No. 175.266, 7/14/54.)</p>
      </content>
